Package com.Akif

Class WordLinkedList

java.lang.Object
com.Akif.WordLinkedList
public class WordLinkedList
extends java.lang.Object
This class is to handle words of a crossword puzzle. Each node keeps a character and references to previous and next nodes. To link the words, each node may have a reference to a cross node, as well.

  • Method Details

    • addCross

      public void addCross​(WordLinkedList other, int itselfIndex, int otherIndex)
      This method adds a cross between itself and another word at specified indexes. The other word should have the corresponding cross, as well.
      Parameters:
      other - other WordLinkedList object to add a cross.
      itselfIndex - index of cross letter(node) in my word
      otherIndex - index of cross letter(node) in other word

    • removeCross

      public void removeCross​(int index)
      This method removes a cross at specified index in my word.
      Parameters:
      index - index of cross letter(node) in my word.

    • print

      public void print()
      This method prints the word, its cross words and cross indexes. It prints the word and its cross words as in the real puzzle.
